body_html: Sorry about the disruption. We recently shuffled around our CI builds. Just took a look and Windows libtensorflow seems to be having some build issues. Will look to fix next week sometime. Also, if you were downloading the builds from TensorFlow Jenkins, that will no longer be where the build artifacts will live. Will post their new location once everything gets settled.
